  ('optometrist-moex-03063', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-aa93ddf5', 'sub-optometrist-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列疾病何者不會有瞳孔紅反射異常的現象？', '["先天性白內障", "嚴重殘餘增生性原發玻璃體增生症（persistent hyperplastic primary vitreous）", "視網膜母細胞腫瘤", "視神經萎縮"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:54+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "3d8d29219809", "answer_pdf_sha1": "34cf84e1e2dc", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106110", "c": "112", "s": "1105", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "低視力學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 36, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
